ative insights that aid in understanding the\nplastic deformation in \\beta-Sn.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2016 20:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2017 02:35:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
