en the rapidly rotating L-dwarfs. Hence, I suggest that time resolved\nimaging polarization should be a potential technique to detect transiting\nexoplanets around L-dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2016 06:31:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 Jul 2016 07:46:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-04"}
