ce\nof pre-processing in isolated groups, along with an additional rapid mechanism\nfor gas removal within larger groups and clusters, perhaps ram-pressure\nstripping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2016 14:58:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 May 2016 19:34:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
